---

<section id="faq" class="py-20 bg-white" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c3">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c5">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-[var(--primary)] uppercase mb-3 block" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c6">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c7">
        Frequently asked <span class="text-[var(--primary)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c8">Questions</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1b2c9">
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq1">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q1">What types of transformers does Elsan Transformer manufacture?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a1">Elsan manufactures four main product types: distribution transformers (25 kVA – 2,500 kVA), power transformers (3.15 MVA – 50 MVA), single phase transformers (up to 160 kVA), and special type transformers including solar/photovoltaic and dual voltage configurations. All products are manufactured to IEC 60076 and relevant international standards.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq2">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q2">Are Elsan transformers compliant with international and Nigerian standards?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a2">
          Yes. All Elsan power and distribution transformers are designed, manufactured, and tested in full compliance with IEC 60076. Our quality management system is certified to ISO 9001, ISO 14001, and ISO 45001. Our products meet Nigerian grid code requirements and are suitable for use by DISCOs and other regulated utilities.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq3">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q3">Can Elsan manufacture transformers to custom specifications?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a3">
          Absolutely. Our engineering team specialises in custom transformer design for non-standard applications. We can tailor voltage ratios, winding configurations, tap changer arrangements, cooling classes, and insulation levels to your exact project requirements. Send us your single-line diagram or technical specification to get started.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q4">Does Elsan supply transformers outside Nigeria?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a4">
          Yes. We actively supply transformers to customers across West Africa including Ghana, Cameroon, Benin Republic, and Niger. Our team handles full export documentation and can advise on logistics to your destination country.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq5">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q5">What cooling options are available for Elsan transformers?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a5">
          We manufacture transformers with ONAN, ONAF, and OFAF cooling for oil-immersed units, as well as AN dry-type options. The appropriate cooling class is selected based on rated capacity, ambient temperature, installation environment, and load profile — all important considerations for Nigerian operating conditions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q6">Do you supply to Electricity Distribution Companies (DISCOs)?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a6">
          Yes. Elsan Transformer actively works with Electricity Distribution Companies and state electricity boards across Nigeria, supplying distribution and power transformers for both new installations and replacement of existing units on the national grid network.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 7 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq7">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q7">What is the lead time for ordering a transformer?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a7">
          Lead times vary depending on product type, rated capacity, and whether the unit is standard or custom-engineered. Contact our engineering team with your requirements and we will provide a confirmed delivery schedule with your quotation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 8 -->
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-[var(--border)]" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:faq8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:q8">How do I request a quotation?</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--text-muted)] leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/home/FAQ.astro:a8">
          Complete our online enquiry form, email our sales team, call us during business hours, or send us a WhatsApp message. Please include your required capacity (kVA/MVA), primary and secondary voltage, quantity, and any special requirements. Our engineering team will respond within one business day.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
